{"tid":1616941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"狗最驚係咩?","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:09:40.000Z","uid":272202,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"02b8627d44cc37f209c69df2f646cb359674cb63","tid":1616941,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"啱先立場live見到 約22:50<br />\n有狗失控拎電筒照鏡頭 阻記者影嘢<br />\n一邊話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你做咩影我地呀?你係咪想起我底?你係咪想起我地底放上網?你影我地係咪想起底?</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇嚟佢地真係好驚驚 淨係起底未有公開證實麻包袋都咁敏感<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>千祈唔好</strong></span></span>引入木蝨、阿強、白蟻等昆蟲去狗宿舍呀<br />\n特別係木蝨 咬完痕到仆街 成晚唔洗訓<br />\n有一家大細真係清極都清唔完<br />\n清完都會成日覺得仲係有蝨咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0a5ff8070c28fc8d5480da7261a87def00d45f","tid":1616941,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:57:36.000Z","msg":"聖水同蟲蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b871e09ed5334b28dfcaf363b562bb0885b85c","tid":1616941,"uid":126476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"邊有咁蠢裝甲對人肉，跟放工等屋企人好難咩"},{"pid":"dd5881b14c03f6bddd854696cf560b2c254dd141","tid":1616941,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:58:19.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEuaWbb7R